title: BRIEF-Gigas Hosting eligible for admission to Spain's alternative market - MAB
text:
BRIEF-Gigas Hosting eligible for admission to Spain's alternative market - MAB Sept 24 
Sept 24 Mercado Alternativo Bursatil (MAB): 
* Gigas Hosting, a cloud computing service provider, receives favorable report from MAB and is eligible for admission to Spain's alternative market Growth Companies segment Source text: bit.ly/1FhJaEP 
(Gdynia Newsroom)
